privacy budget that provides a measure of the privacy loss incurred

by the DP algorithm. The smaller the value of ùúñ, the smaller the

privacy loss (i.e. the stronger the privacy protection) and vice versa. Sensitivity. The sensitivity [23], denoted as Œîùëì , is a measure of

